author: jleroux
msg: A patch from Pierre Smits for "ViewQuoteItemInfo.ftl has at the wrong place" https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OFBIZ-6030

When a product has been added to a quote and subsequently looking at http://demo-trunk-ofbiz.apache.org/ordermgr/control/ViewQuote it shows that the quantity and sel. amount are positioned wrong (1 column to the right of where they should be).
